<asp:Content ID="BodyContent" ContentPlaceHolderID="ContentPlaceHolder1" runat="server">
    <h3>Welcome</h3>

    <p style="text-align:justify;">Library Management System (LMS) is an essential tool for efficiently managing library resources and services at Virtual University. Designed to streamline tasks such as cataloging, circulation, and user management, the LMS at Virtual University enables students, faculty, and staff to access a wide range of digital and physical materials seamlessly. The system offers an intuitive interface for searching, borrowing, and returning books while keeping track of availability and reservations in real-time. By integrating advanced digital technologies, the LMS enhances learning, research, and collaboration, making it a cornerstone of the academic infrastructure at Virtual University.</p>
